This is first version of XJPEGroot.

A simple program for installing images to Your root window.

XJPEGroot support two image formats: JPEG and GIF.

XJPEGroot has two options:
   
    xjpegroot -t file.jpg         Tiling image 'file.jpg' on root window
    
    xjpegroot -c file.jpg         Place image 'file.jpg' in the center of root window
    
XJPEGroot automaticaly detect type of file, so filename can have any name
even without '.jpg' or '.gif' extensions.

PS: XJPEGroot work only on TrueColor Visuals. Other Visuals will be available
       in next version. Sorry!
       
       
       
